data.description: This charming residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by hardwood floors and a warm and spacious living room. The kitchen/dining area is equipped with modern appliances and provides an ideal setting for preparing and enjoying delicious meals with your loved ones. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom, the basement is finished with a full bathroom offering the possibility of a 4th bedroom, second living room or additional storage. Behind the house, there is garage parking.  This home provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Conveniently situated in the Overbrook Park Section, this property offers easy access to shopping centers and transportation options. Whether you're a first-time home-buyer or looking to upgrade your living space.
